headline.print_headline: Bayern Restore Order With 4-0 Drubbing of Paderborn
headline.main: Bayern Restore Order With 4-0 Drubbing of Paderborn

lead_paragraph: Champions Bayern Munich ended Paderborn's dream start to the season with a 4-0 demolition of the Bundesliga newboys on Tuesday, with Mario Goetze netting twice and new signing Robert Lewandowski getting off the mark.
